Common.Highlight.Common.Text: New lease to Orange Theory Fitness

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present units 278 & 279 within the brand new SQ1 development presented by Empire Global. The two units, measuring a total of 254sqm* plus 52sqm* of outdoor space, have recently been leased to Orange Theory Fitness on a brand new 5 + 5 + 5 year term. The first year’s gross rent is $92,000 +GST which increases annually by 3.5%.

SQ1 is a mixed used development which consists of seven modern commercial ground floor units fronting Anketell Street. Located diagonally opposite Bunning’s Warehouse and in close proximity to the Tuggeranong Medical Centre, the Tuggeranong Hyperdome and other major retailers, these units benefits from high levels of passing traffic. 

Key Investment highlights include:

- 254sqm* plus 52sqm* of outdoor space
- 4 secure basement carparks
- Brand new 5 + 5 + 5 year lease to Orange Theory Fitness
- Estimated net income: $78,000p.a*
- Attractive 3.5% annual increases

For more further information or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents of CBRE.

For further information or to arrange for an inspection of this property, please contact the nominated representatives of CB Richard Ellis, Canberra

EOI: Closing Thursday 4, December 2008

Four Seasons House is a three-storey unit titled commercial property prominently situated in the heart of Tuggeranong town centre, directly opposite Tuggeranong Hyperdome and close to all town centre amenities including Canberra Institute of Technology, Lake Tuggeranong College, Limelight Cinema, The Homeworld Centre, Southern Cross Club, AMF Bowling and
Lake Tuggeranong.

- Unit 12 is a fitted out 1,363sqm* office comprising the entire first floor, suitable for office, education or residential conversion

- Units 13-20 comprise a number of tenanted ground floor retail units ranging from 60sqm-109sqm* leased to Planet Max,
Bloomin’ Mad Flowers, Hodgkinson Real Estate and Ace High Eatery - perfect entry level investments

- Units 21-25 comprise several ground floor vacant units ranging from 83sqm-109sqm* suitable for a variety of uses such as office, retail, restaurant and personal services

This is a flexible opportunity to lease or purchase on an individual basis or in parcels of multiple units. 

FOR SALE BY EXPRESSION OF INTEREST 1ST NOVEMBER 2017

For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE the exclusive sales & leasing agents.
